Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Call for Olympics boycott
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w0yk
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Jan 1980
President Carter considers pros and cons of boycotting the coming summer Olympics in Moscow. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less